### VaR Calculation
POST http://localhost:8000/invest/var
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "portfolio": [0.4, 0.6],
  "returns": [
    [0.01, -0.02],
    [0.03, 0.01],
    [-0.01, -0.03]
  ],
  "alpha": 0.95
}

### CVaR Calculation
POST http://localhost:8000/invest/cvar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "portfolio": [0.5, 0.5],
